nodes.text: Halka Four-Den was a female individual who served as an expert commander of a Galactic Republic Alpha Team during the Republic Era. At one point, Halka's Alpha Team was one such unit sent to chart and map the increasing borders of the Republic, and was sent to the planet Dagobah to map and study the world's rare wildlife and fauna. Halka Four-Den kept an account of the unique flora and fauna encountered on Dagobah, including her team's discovery that the knobby white spider later grew into gnarltrees.

Although Halka Four-Den never discovered the Cave of Evil, the team managed to survive for only three months until the deadly diseases, dangerous wildlife, and fast-growing plants depleted and overwhelmed the team. No trace of Commander Halka Four-Den or her Alpha Team was discovered.
